{"tid":430736,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"新手買相機","createTime":"2017-10-10T05:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T08:07:16.000Z","uid":73189,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a728d452be155d61f4d631ddae9490b3cd11bb05","tid":430736,"uid":73189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T05:22:51.000Z","msg":"想問師兄們<br />\n80D<br />\n配呢支鏡得唔得<br />\nEF 24-105mm f/4L IS II USM<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主要影下景同人<br />\n第一次買 屌細力啲<br />\n預算～10000"},{"pid":"8e589acaff2233c4f07eb67764a9b1eb297b66c6","tid":430736,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T05:23:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c516f7b7a1164d1d6d5bdad14b13e95458519a3","tid":430736,"uid":73189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T05:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問師兄們<br />\n80D<br />\n配呢支鏡得唔得<br />\nEF 24-105mm f/4L IS II USM<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主要影下景同人<br />\n第一次買 屌細力啲<br />\n預算～10000<br />\n<br />\n比少少意見<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6aec8fdb5a3c1ac55bd10ffbcee9485199c6573a","tid":430736,"uid":41084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:23:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問師兄們<br />\n80D<br />\n配呢支鏡得唔得<br />\nEF 24-105mm f/4L IS II USM<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主要影下景同人<br />\n第一次買 屌細力啲<br />\n預算～10000</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同樣f／4，24－70嘅成像會比24－105好，而用24－70的話，70打後嘅焦段仲有70－200小小白去carry，唔好貪個105，身邊有FF朋友用24－105都係唔多滿意。<br />\n<br />\nbudget有限，唯有用f／4將就下，不過如果你都既然唔選擇kit嘅話，不如一步到位24－70 f／2.8，用大光圈<br />\n<br />\n留意返80D係APSC機，要x1.6，24廣角端唔會夠廣角<br />\n<br />\n至於機身，唔追求FF嘅話，80D都已經係最全面個部，又或者可以睇埋77D<br />\n<br />\n利申：一開波70D+18－135kit，早排入手24－70 f／2.8，好正影得好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee07002c7366bf057833f1984f8eee71db40b5e","tid":430736,"uid":117044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:33:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0a12afbcd0830ca3d1cefda2c2f0f2b99b2f667","tid":430736,"uid":41084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:46:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>10000淨買鏡?<br />\n80D連24-105唔只1萬,<br />\n我當係1萬淨買鏡:<br />\n<br />\n會買EF16-35 F/2.8L II USM,<br />\n約8千,<br />\n你果支24-105完全唔係對手,<br />\n記得係2代,<br />\n3代成1.5萬你唔夠錢,<br />\n淨低2000蚊,<br />\n買EF 50 F/1.8 STM,<br />\n唔好貪平買非STM版,<br />\n又嘈又慢,<br />\n8佰幾。<br />\n仲有1000蚊買支永諾機頂燈,<br />\n有HSS的款式,<br />\n例如686EX-RT,<br />\n完成任務。<br />\n<br />\nBTW,<br />\n留名睇痴線佬推人買Sony<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新入坑我建議玩住一機一鏡先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，之後先再慢慢入手其他鏡同玩閃<br />\n50 f／1.8 STM 算係必入手，平又有質素，但留意返x1.6 之後都成85mm，標準鏡會變成tele<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n80D 要廣角鏡可以睇下 EF－S 10－22，係幾舊嘅鏡，但自己用落覺得比EF－S 10－18好好多，APSC機要廣角至超廣角唯有睇返EF－S嘅鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n除咗原廠，有d副廠鏡(Tokina, Sigma)都可以睇下，但我本身無入手同用過，俾唔到idea你"},{"pid":"9c975aa0d327baf7f27436735dd15edf801800d4","tid":430736,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:51:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fd92cd2e904402af6860e47d0c547aeeb58753e","tid":430736,"uid":73189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問師兄們<br />\n80D<br />\n配呢支鏡得唔得<br />\nEF 24-105mm f/4L IS II USM<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主要影下景同人<br />\n第一次買 屌細力啲<br />\n預算～10000</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同樣f／4，24－70嘅成像會比24－105好，而用24－70的話，70打後嘅焦段仲有70－200小小白去carry，唔好貪個105，身邊有FF朋友用24－105都係唔多滿意。<br />\n<br />\nbudget有限，唯有用f／4將就下，不過如果你都既然唔選擇kit嘅話，不如一步到位24－70 f／2.8，用大光圈<br />\n<br />\n留意返80D係APSC機，要x1.6，24廣角端唔會夠廣角<br />\n<br />\n至於機身，唔追求FF嘅話，80D都已經係最全面個部，又或者可以睇埋77D<br />\n<br />\n利申：一開波70D+18－135kit，早排入手24－70 f／2.8，好正影得好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果根據巴打所講<br />\n我直接上ff機比較好 <br />\n因為第一次買機 所以想買好少少"},{"pid":"e833e997f674e31677a5836a999254a422005562","tid":430736,"uid":41084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:53:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBTW,<br />\n留名睇痴線佬推人買Sony<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新入坑我建議玩住一機一鏡先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，之後先再慢慢入手其他鏡同玩閃<br />\n50 f／1.8 STM 算係必入手，平又有質素，但留意返x1.6 之後都成85mm，標準鏡會變成tele<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n80D 要廣角鏡可以睇下 EF－S 10－22，係幾舊嘅鏡，但自己用落覺得比EF－S 10－18好好多，APSC機要廣角至超廣角唯有睇返EF－S嘅鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n除咗原廠，有d副廠鏡(Tokina, Sigma)都可以睇下，但我本身無入手同用過，俾唔到idea你</blockquote><br />\n係喎,<br />\n唔記得仲有EFS 10-22,<br />\n唔好買EFS 10-18,差好多,<br />\n咁仲有錢剩買filter喎</blockquote><br />\n10－22唔駛落filter啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186b5bf95f33d2f7a4d760398b64f3c01678b2d5","tid":430736,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:54:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"684c9fd078ca321fedf9bb32ee5a3ea326a1b505","tid":430736,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:55:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07b1cbb93a3f88a25345ae95bad5a559a39801f1","tid":430736,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:56:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5079371599cac31e4f5b0ed458eadd563f25920","tid":430736,"uid":73189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:01:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n如果根據巴打所講<br />\n我直接上ff機比較好 <br />\n因為第一次買機 所以想買好少少</blockquote><br />\n你得一萬點FF body+鏡呀?<br />\n兩萬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網見6d2都賣兩萬內 <br />\n有曬80d功能 又係ff機<br />\n好似好抵屌"},{"pid":"0a01efdf2d84f09c5ada1e107323f08c612586df","tid":430736,"uid":41084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:01:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n如果根據巴打所講<br />\n我直接上ff機比較好 <br />\n因為第一次買機 所以想買好少少</blockquote><br />\n你得一萬點FF body+鏡呀?<br />\n兩萬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直接上FF機首要條件係有budget<br />\n<br />\n考慮6D Mark II body已經$12080<br />\n連EF 24-70mm f/4L IS USM嘅kit $17800<br />\n鏡頭EF 24-70mm f/2.8L II USM 本身$11200<br />\n<br />\n同埋留意返，FF機無內閃，要用閃光燈一定要買埋外置閃光燈"},{"pid":"217b657c60e13802c6c06bb389d8e9d65f8ae27c","tid":430736,"uid":41084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n如果根據巴打所講<br />\n我直接上ff機比較好 <br />\n因為第一次買機 所以想買好少少</blockquote><br />\n你得一萬點FF body+鏡呀?<br />\n兩萬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網見6d2都賣兩萬內 <br />\n有曬80d功能 又係ff機<br />\n好似好抵屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n論機能咁一定直上FF機最好嘅，但除咗機能，都要睇返自己想影相時係輕啲定重啲，想方便定追求高畫質<br />\n<br />\nAgain，APSC機仲有77D可以考慮下<br />\n<br />\nbtw 巴打啱嘅話我可以放部70D比你，當資助我上6D Mark II <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3627b789966e74edc3f04d704b80775eee261e","tid":430736,"uid":41084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:23:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://睇price.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%9D%87price.com.hk&d=6EIVBcTCt3Z5UoWiU1NYWQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=187261f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">睇price.com.hk</a>，Canon EOS 80D 連EF-S 18-55mm f/3.5-5.6 IS STM鏡頭套裝 $7810，起步嚟講都ok"},{"pid":"a3ae623ece0bc0b2ea07852b6484bbc893f27eaf","tid":430736,"uid":73189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:47:40.000Z","msg":"咁如果買6d2 + kit的話<br />\n邊支kit鏡比較好呢？<br />\n<a href=\"http://上price.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B8%8Aprice.com&d=6EIVBcTCt3Z5UoWi